      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEYOND THE LIMITS (3) didn't have any luck on straightening last start with the jock sitting up on him in the straight. Back to an easier level now and maps to get all the favours from a good draw. Tsang's claim comes in handy and he can knock over his maiden win. PRETEY ROYAL (7) hasn't been far away her past couple, including as favourite over the 1720m at this track. Back out to 1900m today is a big tick after a strong performance here two back and Gaerth reunites. Can go one better without surprising. INFRASTRUCTURE (2) led them up over 1720m here last start and now steps out to 1900m again third-up into the campaign. He led and was strong from the front there and can improve again with the added fitness under his belt. Can play a leading role. LAST MILE (4) is knocking on the door and won't be far away from a good barrier. OBSCENTINO (1) is right in this on his best form.",
